          <div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center">About Us</h1>

    <section class="my-4">
      <h2>Who Are We?</h2>
      <p>Craft Connect is a vibrant and dynamic platform designed to empower skilled artisans and connect them with customers who appreciate authentic, handmade craftsmanship. We strive to bridge the gap between talented artisans and local as well as international markets by providing a comprehensive digital marketplace. Our mission is to celebrate handmade artistry, foster artisan growth, and revive traditional crafts with contemporary and marketable designs.</p>
      <p>At Craft Connect, we view artisans as the heart and soul of our community. We go beyond just offering a marketplace by providing marketing support, design consultations, and a platform for their voices to be heard. Our mission is to ensure that artisans receive the recognition and value they truly deserve for their remarkable creations.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="my-4">
      <h2>What We Offer</h2>
      <p>Through our website and mobile app, Craft Connect provides a seamless platform for artisans working independently, from home, or within organized groups. Our goal is to eliminate the middlemen, enabling artisans to earn fair profits and gain direct access to a diverse customer base.</p>
      <p>We also focus on skill development, design consultations, and viable partnerships to help artisans create sustainable businesses. By bringing together ethical businesses and creative minds, Craft Connect fosters a positive and meaningful change in the world of arts and crafts.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="my-4">
      <h2>Vision</h2>
      <p>Our vision is to create a thriving ecosystem that connects every artisan to a global market, touching countless lives in the process and preserving the rich cultural heritage of handmade craftsmanship.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="my-4">
      <h2>Mission</h2>
      <ul class="list-group">
        <li class="list-group-item">Reviving traditional and endangered crafts by blending them with modern aesthetics.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">Economically empowering artisans and women entrepreneurs through skill development, mentorship, and direct market access.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">Promoting fair trade practices and supporting ethical businesses.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">Strengthening intercultural connections and fostering mutual respect and admiration through the celebration of diverse crafts.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="my-4">
      <h2>The Name "Craft Connect"</h2>
      <p>Craft Connect embodies the essence of connection and creativity. The name symbolizes our commitment to linking artisans with the right opportunities and bridging the gap between traditional craftsmanship and modern markets. It represents a journey of hope, collaboration, and the limitless potential of human creativity.</p>
    </section>

    
